<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038490" n="1"/>
<opener> Illustrissimo et Doctissimo Viro <rs key="pers_DE-588-102552517" type="person"><abbr>P.</abbr> <abbr>A.</abbr> <abbr>Michel.</abbr></rs> <abbr>S. P. D.</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person"><abbr>N. B.</abbr></rs> </opener>
<p><lb/>Maximas Tibi ago gratias pro gratulatione Tua propter <subst><del><gap/></del><add>va</add></subst>letudinem
                              <lb/>meam, spero eandem indies melius se habituram; vicissim gaudeo
                              <lb/>Te optime valere, et <add>ut</add> ita pergas opto. Non intelligo dubium Tuum
                              <lb/>circa minimas ellipsis ordinatas, et maximam diametrum particular<choice><orig><g ref="#um">ū</g></orig><reg>um</reg></choice>
                              <lb/>cubicarum, spero tamen illud evaniturum terminis rite intellectis.<del> Quam-</del>
<del><lb/>vis enim minime directo ad Ellipsis axorum sint pro diametris accipien
                                    <lb/>-do, tamen minima ordinata eadem est qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> minima diametra potest esse</del>
<lb/><add>Suspicor</add> quod erraverim ipse, et quia non dantur minim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ordinat<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> Ellipsis pu<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>taverim sermonem esse de minimis diametris, quomodo enim potest h<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>c
                              <lb/>hypothesis formari, quod minima ordinata <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> nulla est<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> major
                              <lb/>vel saltem <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>qualis sit diametro particularum cubicarum? Die <date when="1718-10-28">Sab<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>bathi</date> <rs type="letter">scribam</rs><note type="internal"><!-- Im BIBB erfassen. --></note> ad <rs key="pers_DE-588-118509969" type="person">Patruum</rs> de Tuo proposito, non dubito quin Tibi
    <lb/>favi<subst><del>tet</del><add>turus</add></subst> sit, et <rs key="biblio_EA3M6JGK" type="biblio">lectionem Libri</rs> Tui absoluturus ante pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>sti<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>tutum <choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> Te tempus<subst><del>, siquidem negotia f</del><add>.</add></subst> <rs type="person">Amicus</rs><note type="internal"><!-- ToDo: Person erstellen und verlinken: Unbekannter Freund, hält sich in Locarno auf. --></note> meus<del> haud fac</del> qui
                              <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2659869" type="place">Lucarni</rs> degit haud facile occasionem habebit, cito mittendi<del> Libru</del>
<lb/>scripta Tua <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs>, unde melius fore existimo, ut mittantur
    <lb/>vel<del> ad A</del> <rs key="place_GEO-3173435" type="place">Mediolanum</rs> ad <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1221327275">Agentem</rs> <abbr>D.</abbr> Marchionis <rs key="pers_DE-588-1221327275" type="person">Butintrochi</rs>, vel 
                              <lb/><rs key="place_GEO-2775220" type="place">Oenipontum<del> ad</del> (Inspruc)</rs> ad Amicum aliquem <abbr>Dni</abbr> <rs type="person">de Tassis</rs><note type="internal"><!-- De tassis in Insbruck persontag--></note>, cum
                              <lb/>mandato, ut isti amici solvant expensas pro transmissione <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basileam</rs>
    <lb/>usque. Pro <rs type="biblio" key="biblio_EA3M6JGK">dissertatione de Morbis ab Aucta Circulatione Sanguinis oriun<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>dis</rs>, jam nuper scripsi, eandemque petitionem proxime iterabo.</p> <closer><salute>Vale et
                                          <lb/>me amare perge.</salute> <rs key="place_GEO-3171728" type="place">Patavii</rs> <abbr>d.</abbr> <date when="1718-10-26">26. <abbr>Oct.</abbr> 1718</date>.</closer>
